main event: One object, round, size of head of pin, color bright-green observed stationary in the sky.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 10 minutes,The object was observed approximately 3-5 miles from Norton AFB.,The observer noted that the object resembled a green light similar to a stop light.,The observation was made from Highland Park, N.E. of Los Angeles.,The report concluded that the object was possibly a balloon.
witness description: Civilian observer who reported a stationary green light.
